{
  "text": "Odontoid fractures are frequently associated with head and face trauma and subaxial injuries, and neurological deficits are present in 2% to 27% of the cases [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Between 25% and 40% of the patients with cervical fractures that were the result of high-energy traumas are lost at the scene [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
